Package com.oracle.tools.runtime.coherence

Class Summary
Cluster A Cluster represents an Coherence Cluster as an ApplicationGroup.
ClusterBuilder A ClusterBuilder is a Coherence specific ApplicationGroupBuilder for Coherence Clusters.
ClusterMember A ClusterMember is a specialized SimpleJavaApplication to represent Coherence-based Cluster Members at runtime.
ClusterMemberSchema A ClusterMemberSchema is a Coherence-based specific JavaApplicationSchema.
 

Enum Summary
ClusterMemberSchema.JMXManagementMode The Management enumeration specifies the valid JMX Management Modes for a cluster node.
